SELECT m.id, 'Welcome', 'welcome', '<h2>Welcome</h2><p>It is my pleasure to welcome you as you embark on your journey with Innovative Air Technologies. I am delighted to have you join our dynamic team of professionals.</p><p>At Innovative Air Technologies, we pride ourselves on being leaders in the field of industrial desiccant dehumidifiers. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and enriching the lives of our customers has given us a competitive advantage in the industry. As a Sales Representative, you play a vital role in our continued success and growth.</p><p>In this Sales Representative Onboarding Manual, you will find valuable insights, resources, and tools to equip you for success in your role. From understanding our product line to mastering sales techniques, we are dedicated to providing you with the support and guidance you need to thrive in your position.</p><p>Our company culture is built on our core values and as you become part of the Innovative Air Technologies family, you will discover a supportive and collaborative environment where your contributions are valued and recognized.</p><p>I encourage you to embrace this opportunity with enthusiasm and determination. Together, we will achieve great things and continue to exceed the expectations of our customers.</p><p>Once again, welcome to Innovative Air Technologies. I look forward to witnessing your growth and success with us.</p><p>Warm regards,<br><strong>Kacy</strong></p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Kacy welcome video embed — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure>', 0, TRUE, 3
