SELECT m.id, 'Meet the Team', 'meet-the-team', '<h2>Meet the Team</h2><h3>Kacy Orr, President</h3><p>Meet Kacy, the driving force behind Innovative Air Technologies. With a keen eye for the future, he meticulously crafts our strategic vision. Passionate about sales and engineering, Kacy ensures that IAT delivers comprehensive solutions to our customers'' humidity challenges, fostering enduring relationships. His journey began at Low Humidity Systems under his father''s guidance before founding Innovative Air Technologies in 2001.</p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Video — Meet Kacy Orr, President of Innovative Air Technologies — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure><h3>David Schurk, National Sales Manager</h3><p>DEE, CEM, LEED-AP, CGNA, CWEP, SFP, CIAQM. David is National Sales Manager for Innovative Air Technologies in Covington, GA. He also serves as an ASHRAE Distinguished Lecturer, is an ASHRAE Life Member, and Committee Chair for the ASHE Sustainability and Decarbonization Leadership Task Force. He has over 40 years of experience in the design and analysis of heating, ventilating, and air-conditioning systems for a variety of market sectors, with a special focus on healthcare and aerospace environmental control and air quality.</p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Video — Meet David Schurk — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure><h3>Crystal Hill, Director of Operations</h3><p>Crystal has been with Innovative Air Technologies since its inception in 2001. She began her career working for Low Humidity Systems. She has 22+ years combined in customer service and all areas of office functions. She is an excellent multi-tasker and works hard to ensure all tasks are successfully completed.</p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Video — Crystal Hill, Director of Operations — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure><h3>James Pope, Director of Engineering &amp; Production</h3><p>James grew up on the East Coast of Canada and holds degrees in Civil Engineering from New Brunswick Community College &amp; Old Dominion University. James moved to the US with his family in 2010. His love for engineering started at a young age as he completed electronic projects with his grandfather. After 20 years of engineering experience, his passion to design and create continues to grow.</p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Video — Meet James Pope, Director of Engineering &amp; Production — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure><h3>Summer Neal, Marketing Manager</h3><p>Summer is a versatile professional with a diverse background. After 22 years as a dental hygienist, she transitioned her career to pursue her passion for marketing by obtaining a BS in Strategic Communications from Liberty University (2022). Summer oversees Innovative Air Technologies marketing efforts, including branding, website, digital and print media and social media.</p><figure class="img-missing"><figcaption>📷 Image from Trainual: Video — Meet Summer, your friendly neighborhood Marketing Manager — re-upload via admin editor</figcaption></figure><h3>Jerry Orr, Humidity Consultant</h3><p>If you are ever looking for someone who has experienced it all, look no further than Jerry. He has over 50 years of experience in the desiccant dehumidification and humidity control field. Jerry owned and operated Low Humidity Systems from 1981–2001 when he decided to semi-retire and come to work for IAT as a humidity consultant.</p>', 1, TRUE, 5
